About

Where Does the Money Go?

$13,000+tax goes to purchasing the tuba. Plus an additional charge for a new mouthpiece. The tuba is a Perantucci Model PT6 CC. However, I am willing to spend much less on a tuba if I can find a similar quality used horn. And then put more money toward funding the album work and equipment for the recording process. In addition, I will need new notation software to continue writing original music
